title: Justin Martin
text:
Justin Martin (born April 20, 1979) is an <a href="Americans">American</a> DJ and record producer, based in <a href="San%20Francisco">San Francisco</a>.
Career.
Martin released his sophomore album on April 20, 2016, via Dirtybird Records.
In 2020, Martin launched his own label, What To Do…, with the single “Needs.”
